<span class="n">sharing</span><span class="p">.</span>
</pre></div>
<p>See also <a class="alink" href="/p/whonix/wiki/Security%20Guide/">[Security Guide]</a>.</p>
<h1 id="further-security">Further Security</h1>
<p>If this article gets updated, the following should be noted:</p>
<p><a class="" href="http://kb.vmware.com/selfservice/microsites/search.do?language=en_US&amp;cmd=displayKC&amp;externalId=1541" rel="nofollow">Changing or keeping a UUID for a moved virtual machine</a></p>
<p><strong>"The UUID is based on the physical computer's identifier and the path to the virtual machine's configuration file."</strong></p>
